steps.commandline:
rm CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info

sizeR1=$(du ${SAMPLE}_1.fastq | cut -d'	' -f 1)
sizeR2=$(du ${SAMPLE}_2.fastq | cut -d'	' -f 1)

echo "size R1 (KB) = $sizeR1" >> CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info
echo "size R2 (KB) = $sizeR2" >> CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info
echo "R1 equal R2 = "$(if [ $sizeR1 -eq $sizeR2 ]; then echo "true"; else echo "false"; fi) >> CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info
echo "#read R1 = "$(wc -l ${SAMPLE}_1.fastq | cut -d' ' -f 1 | awk '{print $1/4}') >> CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info
echo "#read R2 = "$(wc -l ${SAMPLE}_2.fastq | cut -d' ' -f 1 | awk '{print $1/4}') >> CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info

python $BASEDIR/monitor.py -m single -s CheckDownload -i $SAMPLE -f CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.info -t "key-value" > CheckDownload-$SAMPLE.json
steps.title: CheckDownload
